{"tid":700223,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆啟動】中小銀行或最快月底加P","createTime":"2018-06-13T07:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T12:39:27.000Z","uid":163207,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e10e1bf44715554a50deb8ee90a1ae641671b1d7","tid":700223,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180613/58311654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F58311654&d=HAZdIaBCQoHtnCf8pRKwwKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5e2dc2f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F58311654&h=d80c2517\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180613/58311654</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple Daily<br />\n焦點<br />\n全部<br />\n要聞<br />\n突發<br />\n娛樂<br />\n兩岸<br />\n國際<br />\n財經<br />\n果籽<br />\n體育<br />\n賽馬<br />\nWONDER<br />\n壹週刊<br />\n飲食男女<br />\nKetchuper<br />\n主頁<br />\n即時<br />\n動新聞<br />\n日報<br />\n周刊<br />\n即時分類<br />\n焦點<br />\n全部<br />\n要聞<br />\n突發<br />\n娛樂<br />\n兩岸<br />\n國際<br />\n財經<br />\n果籽<br />\n體育<br />\n賽馬<br />\nWONDER<br />\n壹週刊<br />\n飲食男女<br />\nKetchuper<br />\n <br />\n【加息週期】中小銀行或最快月底加P<br />\n5小時前4.7K<br />\n即時財經<br />\n <br />\n中小銀行認為本港已具上調最優惠利率（P）條件。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n美聯儲局週四凌晨將公布議息結果，市場料會後加息0.25厘的機會達百份百。中原按揭經紀董事總經理王美鳳認為，香港銀行加息的基本條件已出現，銀行結餘雖然減少了700多億元，但仍在千億元水平，所以對大型銀行來說加息壓力較中小型銀行要少，故預料或有中小型銀行率先上調新造按息或封頂息率以紓緩息差受壓之影響，料2至3個月內個P按都可能會加，料全年加幅或達兩次及半厘。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟日報》報道，中小銀行認為本港已具上調最優惠利率（P）條件，最快6月底可以加P；惟大型銀行因銀行體系結餘仍高，對加P未逼切需要。<br />\n<br />\n近期拆息接連上升，1個月拆息連升11日，至1.53429厘，為近十年高；3個月拆息逼近2厘，報1.99321厘。"},{"pid":"af7e3edff95c444e719c40432aaba5cbda6aadcb","tid":700223,"uid":163207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"淡友軍們準備好花生未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b30b2c416563f47753b5f57a32cec7b8495d5a","tid":700223,"uid":1441,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"有壓力測試，驚乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f32ca0dc3834b57ecd8865bfd8b477cfd59ad2","tid":700223,"uid":158613,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"林鄭已經準備好用空置稅支撐樓市"},{"pid":"a509186473591bfe48d19271d76d9cfadc42dc3d","tid":700223,"uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"放心點都唔會爆"},{"pid":"4b9fa0ed629300f4ccedae74fccf4197b04fcedc","tid":700223,"uid":40207,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0062cbad52eff3c105cc292f32555c2cb3de05","tid":700223,"uid":44646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"大行唔加，中小銀加就等於自殺"},{"pid":"9cd4cc6d525bdf24ba924aa1f3db846d6526aed0","tid":700223,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"利好消息黎 爆咩<br />\n業主又可以加租啦"},{"pid":"8e6d3d5ba2a80146e28ac711517b9048554ae98a","tid":700223,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"供緊樓樓 但希望佢快d加息<br />\n穩定經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a19fab3b3dfbc956532fcd42f6697613b9eb61","tid":700223,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0062cbad52eff3c105cc292f32555c2cb3de05","tid":700223,"uid":44646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"大行唔加，中小銀加就等於自殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"唔做大行，好明顯係d數有問題，<br />\n加個.25 唔會死既<br />\n加1都未死"},{"pid":"0c9e0081387a4cc988e69ad388a34cf08e5f51f